---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="常见问题解答 - 工具门户网站" 
  description="查看用户最常遇到的问题和详细解答，包括工具使用、网站功能、技术支持等方面"
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- 页面标题 -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">常见问题解答</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        查看用户最常遇到的问题和详细解答，快速解决您的疑问
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 快速导航 -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">问题分类</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <a href="#general" class="flex items-center p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-100 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mr-3">ℹ️</span>
            <span class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 font-medium">一般问题</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#tools" class="flex items-center p-4 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-100 dark:hover:bg-green-900/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mr-3">🔍</span>
            <span class="text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 font-medium">工具相关</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#technical" class="flex items-center p-4 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-100 dark:hover:bg-purple-900/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mr-3">⚡</span>
            <span class="text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 font-medium">技术问题</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#security" class="flex items-center p-4 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-100 dark:hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 mr-3">🛡️</span>
            <span class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 font-medium">安全隐私</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 一般问题 -->
    <section id="general" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
        <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">ℹ️</span>
        一般问题
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">❓</span>
              这个网站是做什么的？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              我们的工具门户网站是一个专业的在线工具发现和推荐平台。我们汇集了各个领域的优质工具，包括开发、设计、生产力、学习、安全等分类，帮助用户快速找到适合自己需求的工具。
            </p>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 mb-2">主要功能：</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 space-y-1">
                <li>• 工具分类浏览和搜索</li>
                <li>• 专业工具推荐和评测</li>
                <li>• 详细的功能描述和使用指南</li>
                <li>• 用户友好的界面和体验</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">❓</span>
              使用这个网站需要注册吗？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              不需要！我们的网站完全免费使用，无需注册或登录。您可以直接浏览和发现各种工具，没有任何使用限制。
            </p>
            <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mr-2">✔️</span>
                <span class="text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 font-medium">完全免费，无需注册</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">❓</span>
              网站上的工具都是免费的吗？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              我们收录的工具包含免费和付费两种类型。每个工具的描述中会注明其定价模式，包括：
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 mb-2">完全免费</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">无需付费即可使用全部功能</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 mb-2">免费增值</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">基础功能免费，高级功能付费</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 mb-2">付费工具</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">需要付费订阅或购买</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">❓</span>
              如何推荐新的工具？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              我们非常欢迎用户推荐优秀的工具！您可以通过以下方式推荐：
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm">1</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">通过联系表单</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">访问我们的联系页面，填写工具推荐表单</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm">2</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">发送邮件</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">直接发送邮件到我们的推荐邮箱</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm">3</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">社交媒体</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">在我们的社交媒体账号下留言推荐</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 工具相关问题 -->
    <section id="tools" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
        <span class="mr-3 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">🔍</span>
        工具相关问题
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">❓</span>
              工具的质量如何保证？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              我们对每个收录的工具都有严格的筛选标准：
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">基础筛选</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>工具必须能够正常访问和使用</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>具有明确的功能定位和用途</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>用户界面友好，易于使用</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">质量评估</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>功能完整性和稳定性</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>用户评价和市场口碑</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>更新频率和维护状态</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">❓</span>
              发现工具无法使用怎么办？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              如果您发现某个工具无法正常使用，请按照以下步骤处理：
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300 mb-2">1. 检查网络连接</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400">确保您的网络连接正常，可以尝试访问其他网站</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300 mb-2">2. 检查工具状态</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400">查看工具是否显示为"活跃"状态，或者是否有维护通知</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300 mb-2">3. 联系支持</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400">如果问题持续存在，请通过我们的联系页面报告问题</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">❓</span>
              如何查看工具的详细信息？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              每个工具卡片都包含了丰富的信息：
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">基本信息</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 工具名称和图标</li>
                  <li>• 功能描述</li>
                  <li>• 分类标签</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">状态信息</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 活跃状态</li>
                  <li>• 推荐标识</li>
                  <li>• 权重排序</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">扩展信息</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 相关使用指南</li>
                  <li>• 最佳实践建议</li>
                  <li>• 用户反馈和评价</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 技术问题 -->
    <section id="technical" class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
        <span class="mr-3 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">⚡</span>
        技术问题
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">❓</span>
              网站支持哪些浏览器？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              我们的网站支持所有现代浏览器，包括：
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">桌面浏览器</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Chrome 80+</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Firefox 75+</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Safari 13+</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Edge 80+</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">移动浏览器</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>iOS Safari 13+</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Chrome Mobile 80+</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Samsung Internet 11+</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✔️</span>
                    <span>Firefox Mobile 75+</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">❓</span>
              网站加载缓慢怎么办？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              如果您遇到网站加载缓慢的问题，可以尝试以下解决方案：
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 mb-2">检查网络连接</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 确保您的网络连接稳定</li>
                  <li>• 尝试刷新页面或重启路由器</li>
                  <li>• 检查是否有其他设备占用大量带宽</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300 mb-2">清理浏览器缓存</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 清除浏览器缓存和Cookie</li>
                  <li>• 尝试使用浏览器的无痕模式</li>
                  <li>• 禁用可能干扰的浏览器扩展</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 mb-2">联系技术支持</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 space-y-1">
                  <li>• 如果问题持续存在，请联系我们的技术支持</li>
                  <li>• 提供您的浏览器版本和操作系统信息</li>
                  <li>• 描述具体的加载问题和时间</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">❓</span>
              网站在移动设备上显示异常？
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              我们的网站采用响应式设计，应该能在所有设备上正常显示。如果遇到问题：
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">基本排查</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">✔️</span>
                    <span>尝试旋转屏幕或调整浏览器窗口大小</span>
